          <link xlink:href="ttps://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15163413"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>Like Cebpa, ectopic expression in B cells induces their reprogramming into to macrophage.
[Xie H et al. Cell. 2004 May 28;117(5):663-76]</comment>
      </annotation>
      <nodevisualsetting x="231" y="511" style="Mac"/>
    </node>
