          <link xlink:href=""/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>Ruequired for early hematopoiesis.</comment>
      </annotation>
      <nodevisualsetting x="361" y="181" style="Progenitor"/>
    </node>
    <node id="Gfi1" name="Gfi1" maxvalue="1">
      <value val="1">
        <exp str="(Ikzf1 | Cebpa) &amp; !Egr2"/>
        <exp str="Pax5_prot_active"/>
      </value>
      <annotation>
        <linklist>
          <link xlink:href="http://www.ensembl.org/Mus_musculus/Gene/Summary?db=core;g=ENSMUSG00000029275;r=5:107716657-107726036"/>
          <link xlink:href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19818654"/>
          <link xlink:href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/20453161"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>Promote B cell fate versus myeloid in MPP 
[﻿Spooner et al. (2009) Immunity 31:576-86]

Necessary for B cell development through Id2 inhibition ﻿
[Li et al. (2010) Blood 116:1060-9]
</comment>
      </annotation>
      <nodevisualsetting x="581" y="358" style="Bcell"/>
    </node>
    <node id="Ikzf1" name="Ikzf1" maxvalue="1">
      <value val="1">
        <exp str="Mef2c"/>
        <exp str="Pax5_prot_active"/>
      </value>
      <annotation>
        <linklist>
          <link xlink:href="http://www.ensembl.org/Mus_musculus/Gene/Summary?db=core;g=ENSMUSG00000018654;r=11:11685003-11772926"/>
          <link xlink:href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/7923373"/>
          <link xlink:href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/16518393"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>Necessary for lymphoid development.   
[Georgopoulos K et al. (1994) Cell, 79(1), 143–56]

Necessary for the specification of LMPP from MPP.
[Yoshida T et al.(2006) Nature immunology, 7(4)]

</comment>
      </annotation>
      <nodevisualsetting x="512" y="295" style="Progenitor"/>
    </node>
