          <link xlink:href=""/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>Required for lymphoid development.</comment>
      </annotation>
      <nodevisualsetting x="764" y="422" style="Bcell"/>
    </node>
    <node id="Il7ra" name="IL7R" maxvalue="1">
      <value val="1">
        <exp str="Spi1 &amp; Mef2c &amp; !(Cebpa | Cebpb)"/>
        <exp str="Ebf1 &amp; Foxo1 &amp; !(Cebpa | Cebpb)"/>
      </value>
      <annotation>
        <linklist>
          <link xlink:href="http://www.ensembl.org/Mus_musculus/Gene/Summary?db=core;g=ENSMUSG00000003882;r=15:9506161-9529876;t=ENSMUST00000003981"/>
          <link xlink:href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15837809"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>Necessary for lymphoid differentiation.

KO block B cell development at the preproB stage, Partially rescued by overexpression of EBF or STAT5.
[﻿K. Kikuchi et al., The Journal of experimental medicine 201, 1197-203 (2005)]
</comment>
      </annotation>
      <nodevisualsetting x="932" y="341" style="Bcell"/>
    </node>
