          <link xlink:href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18538592"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>Necessary for normal LMPP/CLP/Lymphoid development  
[﻿Dias, S. et al. (2008)  Immunity, 29(2)]

Necessary to maintain B cell phenotype in proB (rescued by Pax5 constitutive expression)  
[Kwon, K.et al. (2008) Immunity, (June), 751–762]


</comment>
      </annotation>
      <nodevisualsetting x="706" y="382" style="Bcell (small)"/>
    </node>
