          <link xlink:href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/10524622"/>
          <link xlink:href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/10572073"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>Necessary for terminal B cell differentiation.

Knock-out block B cell development at proB stage 
[Nutt, S.L. et al., Nature 401, 556-62 (1999)]

Overexpression in CMP block myeloid differentiation 
[﻿Chiang MY, Monroe JG (1999) Blood 94:3621-32]
</comment>
      </annotation>
      <nodevisualsetting x="861" y="624" style="Bcell (small)"/>
    </node>
